POWER_SAVING_UWB_ON: P1 Power Saving measure Uwb activated
POWER_SAVING_REDUCE_GNSS_ON: P2 Power Saving measure reducing update freq activated
POWER_SAVING_RF_ON: P3 Power Saving measure RF activated
POWER_SAVING_GNSS_ON: P3 Power Saving measure GNSS activated
POWER_SAVING_UWB_OFF: P1 Power Saving measure Uwb deactivated
POWER_SAVING_REDUCE_GNSS_OFF: P2 Power Saving measure reducing update freq deactivated
POWER_SAVING_RF_OFF: P3 Power Saving measure RF deactivated
POWER_SAVING_GNSS_OFF: P3 Power Saving measure GNSS deactivated
HIGH_WARNING_ZONE: Static alarm: name HIGH WARNING ZONE
MEDIUM_WARNING_ZONE: Static alarm: name MEDIUM WARNING ZONE
LOW_WARNING_ZONE: Static alarm: name LOW WARNING ZONE
NONE_WARNING_ZONE: Static alarm: name NONE WARNING ZONE
